  "title": "Cloud Consultant(AWS)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is seeking an experienced Lead to lead the end-to-end onboarding of new AWS accounts and workloads into our AWS Landing Zone environment with AWS Control Tower.</p>\n<p>You will ensure that new AWS account is provisioned and configured in accordance to compliance, security, and governance standards and policies.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Scope:</p>\n<p>Onboarding Process Management</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage the AWS account onboarding process by working closely with application, operations and security teams to understand requirements and timelines.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Account Provisioning &amp; Configuration</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee AWS account creation ensuring all baseline controls (GuardDuty, Security Hub, IAM, CloudTrail) are enforced as part of Infrastructure as Code.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that the configurations and restrictions of network connectivity (VPC, Transit Gateway)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Compliance &amp; Security Assurance</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Validate Security Best Practices are met before handover.</li>\n  <li>Conduct security reviews for compliance posture and remediation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Stakeholder Communication</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Act as POC for onboarding-related queries, updating onboarding status updates to stakeholders and management and maintaining onboarding documentation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Continuous Improvement</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify and implement process improvements, automation opportunities, and efficiency gains in onboarding workflows with DevOps teams to embed automation pipelines for account setup.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Enterprise scale IT operations, cloud service delivery, or project management (AWS experience preferred).</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of AWS Control Tower, AWS Organizations, IAM, networking, and core security services.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with CIS Benchmarks, AWS Well-Architected Framework, and security best practices.</li>\n  <li>Proven ability to manage structured workflows and process documentation.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills for working with both technical and non-technical audiences.</li>\n  <li>Technical exposure in Infrastructure-as-Code (Terraform, CloudFormation); CI/CD pipelines (Jenkins, GitLab CI); Security &amp; compliance (IAM, Security Hub, AWS Config).</li>\n  <li>AWS Certified Solutions Architect or other relevant AWS certifications</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p>\n<p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : kelvin@starcareerconsulting.com</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Kelvin (Reg. No. R1872625)</p>\n<p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
